# ==============================================================================
# 最強肉體 (Ultimate Physique) - Global Constitution & AI Execution Rules
# Current Temporal Context: 2026 | Environment: Cursor AI (Bruce) Focus Protocol
# ==============================================================================

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# SECTION 1: TOKEN FIREWALL & DIRECTORY ISOLATION (極致節能與防線鎖定)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Primary_Workspace: "up-final"
ReadOnly_References: ["reference-app", "reference-app-fitness", "lbj-goat-meter"]

AI_Context_Restriction:
  - Your execution, analysis, and autocomplete context MUST be strictly limited to the `up-final` directory.
  - NEVER run active codebase indexing, global semantic searches, or automatic cross-project scanning on sibling reference directories.
  - You are strictly forbidden from reading, referencing, or analyzing files in reference directories unless the user explicitly invokes them using pinpoint tokens (e.g., @filename).
  - Maintain a zero-token-waste policy. Keep responses concise, targeted, and highly decoupled.

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# SECTION 2: BUSINESS MODEL & ACCESS CONTROL CONSTITUTION (商業模式與權限憲法)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Product_Branding:
  Official_Name: "最強肉體 (Ultimate Physique)"

Business_Architecture:
  Core_Tier: "One-time purchase. Unlocks ALL local features (Assessment pages, 6-axis radar, personal detailed history, local tools, widgets)."
  Pro_Tier: "Monthly subscription. Unlocks Firestore global leaderboard interaction, cloud synchronization, and remote telemetry."

Local_First_Mandate:
  - Detailed physical logs, training history, arm-size, and grip-strength data must remain FULLY FUNCTIONAL locally without any subscription.
  - Personal history screens and snapshot storage must NEVER be locked behind a Pro paywall.

Access_Control_Enforcement:
  - Centralize all entitlement verification inside `src/logic/core/entitlement.ts`.
  - Global leaderboard submission or remote data fetch actions require strict and explicit verification of Pro status.

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# SECTION 3: CLOUD GUARDRAILS & PERFORMANCES (Firebase 成本與效能防禦)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Firebase_Cost_Guardrails:
  - Non-Pro or anonymous guest users MUST NOT generate any Firestore leaderboard read/write traffic.
  - Leaderboard collections must store lightweight summary shards only (best score, minimal profile bucket fields).
  - Rigid enforcement of client-side caching (TTL session cache) and write throttling (rolling hourly limits per shard) is mandatory.

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# SECTION 4: ENGINEERING CULTURE & ARCHITECTURE DISCIPLINE (工程文化與架構準則)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Architecture_Decoupling:
  - Strictly maintain clean separation across layers: `logic` (pure calculations) / `services` (SDK/infra) / `stores` (state) / `hooks` (facades) / `components` (UI).
  - UI components must remain strictly presentational. Business logic, mathematical conversions, and Firebase SDK calls must never leak into components.

Industry_Benchmarks:
  - Do not reinvent standard product patterns. Align UX interactions, screen rendering, off-screen optimization, and state management mechanics with world-class apps such as Spotify, Instagram, and Strava.

Deep_Documentation_Standard:
  - When writing complex or non-trivial engineering logic, code comments MUST clearly document the **"Design Intent (WHY)"** rather than merely describing the **"Action (WHAT)"**.

Structural_Review_Trigger:
  - If any single feature, bug, or calculation function undergoes more than 3 consecutive hotfixes or demonstrates architectural divergence, stop immediately and flag for a full refactoring audit.

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# SECTION 5: EVOLUTIONARY ROADMAP (計分與雷達演進)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scoring_Mandate:
  - Harmonize and preserve the existing arm-size leaderboard formula.
  - Fully integrate the extended grip-strength evaluation tiers into the radar metrics catalog.
  - The core canvas radar component must natively support and cleanly map across exactly 6 active dimensions.